<title>CHINA: C.LYONNAIS PLANS WARRANTS ON PROPERTY STOCKS.</title>
<headline>C.LYONNAIS PLANS WARRANTS ON PROPERTY STOCKS.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-08-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Lyonnais Financial Products (Guernsey) Ltd said on Thursday it proposed to issue one billion American-style call warrants on a basket of property stocks.</p>
<p>Each basket comprises of:</p>
<p> Cheung Kong (Holdings) Ltd	    0.0075 shares</p>
<p> Henderson Land Development Co Ltd   0.0090 shares</p>
<p> Concord Land Development co Ltd     0.0390 shares</p>
<p> HKR International Ltd		   0.0360 shares</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one basket.</p>
<p>Indicative terms:</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    HK$2.0959    PREMIUM	 18.76 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     HK$0.067     GEARING	 3.48x</p>
<p> EXPIRATION	11 MTHS	LISTING DATE  TO BE ANNOUNCED</p>
<p> LISTING	   HONG KONG    PAYDATE	 TO BE ANNOUNCED</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  HK$2.32875   MIN EXER LOT  20,000</p>
<p> SETTLEMENT	CASH SETTLEMENT OR PHYSICAL DELIVERY OF</p>
<p>		     STOCKS AT ISSUER'S DISCRETION</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong News Room (852) 2843 6370</p>
